description: Want to try something differentwith your nails. If you feel its time to experiment with your manicure to switch up your look, then these polishes are for you. This  set comes with 6 different colors, all metallic and glossy, and a magnetic stamp with 6 different designs. Made from materials imported from Paris, this magnetic manicure set is high quality, long-lasting, and gorgeous.
title: SHANY Cosmetics Magnetic Nail Polish, Earth Colors, 14.6 Ounce
